        },
        {
            "+content": "Melody is a reincarnated former Japanese girl who now pursues her dream in her new life, working as an all-purpose maid for a poor count's family in the kingdom of Théolas. When she makes it, even cheap tea becomes a luxury brew and a dilapidated mansion is quickly restored to being new. Cleaning, serving, hunting, DIY—leave it all to her and her powerful magic. Unbeknownst to Melody, this world is an otome game; she is the most powerful and invincible heroine, the saint. Yet, she remains oblivious to this fact.",
